Extreme World is a new season of coverage on the BBC examining the global differences that divide us. Over the next few months we will explore eight key themes that illustrate the contrasts in our extreme world. They include click Hot and Cold, Corruption, Dying, Crime, Education, Business, Pollution and God. Show less